<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>5 Ways to Kill Your Startup"s "Office Politics" Before They Start</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="5 Ways to Kill Your Startup's 'Office Politics' Before They Start" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160225181142-dog-wrong-bad-mistake-paint.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
